    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The exterior is in great shape overall, though you will find some minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of any major wear or odors, with all electronics and climate controls functioning as they should. It runs smoothly and has a documented service history, making it a reliable choice for its next owner who values a solid, honest car.",
