    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This expertly maintained vehicle offers a sophisticated blend of performance and reliability. It has been subjected to a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure mechanical excellence and aesthetic integrity. Featuring a clean history and a well-appointed cabin, this motorcar represents an exceptional value proposition for those seeking a premium driving experience without the new-car depreciation. We invite serious inquiries to experience the refined handling and superior craftsmanship of this distinguished model.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my reliable ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape, well-loved, and totally ready for its next adventure with a new owner! It runs beautifully and would make a perfect daily driver for anyone looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road. I've taken good care of it, and I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 997.1 Carrera S features the venerable 3.8L M97 flat-six power plant, delivering 355 hp with the linear power delivery unique to Porsche\u2019s naturally aspirated engineering. The 6-speed manual transaxle is paired with a short-shift kit for enhanced gate precision and tactile feedback. Equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), the chassis offers adjustable damping to suit both spirited canyon runs and highway cruising. Recent preventative maintenance includes an IMS bearing retrofit and a new rear main seal, addressing critical failure points in the rotating assembly. The braking system retains its factory four-piston monobloc calipers, providing exceptional thermal dissipation and pedal modulation. A mechanically robust example ready for the open road.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Reliable vehicle. Good condition. Well-maintained engine. Clean interior. Minimal wear. Firm price.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine with only minor, age-appropriate road wear that does not detract from its commanding presence. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and free of tears, while all electronic interfaces\u2014from the responsive navigation system to the multi-zone climate control\u2014function exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule, with a comprehensive folder of receipts to prove its pedigree. The tires have ample tread, the brakes are sharp, and the engine delivers smooth, consistent power. This is an ideal choice for a discerning buyer who values a vehicle that has been treated with genuine care and is ready for immediate, dependable use.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional opportunity to acquire a well-maintained vehicle that exemplifies mechanical reliability and sophisticated performance. This unit has been held to a high standard of care, featuring a documented service history and a clean, professional presentation throughout. Engineered for longevity and a refined driving experience, it offers a significant value proposition for the discerning motorist who demands quality without compromise.",
      "price": 36500.0,
