    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a high-revving valvetrain. Mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain sends power to a variable M-differential for optimal traction. Mechanical highlights include a reinforced rear subframe, a refreshed VANOS system, and upgraded bushings for precise lateral kinematics. The chassis remains rigid, and the suspension geometry provides the communicative feedback expected from this iconic platform. Recently serviced with a comprehensive valve adjustment and new rod bearings\u2014essential preventative maintenance for peak performance and longevity.",
